          "30078:<PUBKEY>:cartographers-instrument:feature:solar-resonator"
        ],
        [
          "feature",
          "30078:<PUBKEY>:cartographers-instrument:feature:solar-chart"
        ]
      ],
      "content": "Brass instruments and crystal prisms fill this chamber, arranged in precise geometric patterns. Where the starlight strikes the prisms, faint rainbows scatter across the walls. The brass fittings are etched with solar trajectories and harmonic intervals.\n\nA tall brass framework stands at the room's centre — an armillary sphere with tuning forks where the celestial rings should be."
    },
    {
      "kind": 30078,
      "tags": [
        [
          "d",
